<section class="hero min-h-[40vh] bg-gradient-to-br from-accent/10 to-base-200 rounded-xl mb-10 flex items-center justify-center shadow-lg">
  <div class="text-center">
    <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
      <div class="bg-accent/20 rounded-full p-4 inline-block">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-12 w-12 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" />
        </svg>
      </div>
    </div>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-accent mb-2">About Genderbase</h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-base-content/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">A community-driven platform dedicated to providing accurate, supportive information about gender identity, expression, and diversity.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8 max-w-4xl">
  <div class="prose lg:prose-xl max-w-none">
    <p class="mb-4">Genderbase is a community-driven platform dedicated to providing accurate, supportive information about gender identity, expression, and diversity. Our mission is to create a safe space where people can learn about gender, and find answers to their questions.</p>

    <div class="alert bg-base-200 border-l-4 border-accent/60 mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 17l4 4 4-4m0-5V3m-8 8v6a2 2 0 002 2h4a2 2 0 002-2v-6" />
      </svg>
      <span>Founded in 2025 by <a href="https://dave.io" class="link link-accent">Dave Williams</a></span>
    </div>

    <p class="mb-4">Read our <%= link_to "Good Faith policy", home_good_faith_path, class: "text-base-content/80 hover:text-accent transition font-semibold underline underline-offset-4" %> to understand how we handle questions.</p>

    <div class="divider my-8 before:bg-accent/20 after:bg-accent/20">Our Values</div>

    <ul class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
      <li class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4 shadow flex items-start gap-3"><span class="badge badge-accent badge-outline mt-1 whitespace-nowrap text-sm">Respect</span> We honor all gender identities and expressions without judgment.</li>
      <li class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4 shadow flex items-start gap-3"><span class="badge badge-accent badge-outline mt-1 whitespace-nowrap text-sm">Grace</span> We answer questions posed in good faith without judgment, even if they may accidentally offend.</li>
      <li class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4 shadow flex items-start gap-3"><span class="badge badge-accent badge-outline mt-1 whitespace-nowrap text-sm">Accuracy</span> We are committed to providing factual, unbiased information.</li>
      <li class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4 shadow flex items-start gap-3"><span class="badge badge-accent badge-outline mt-1 whitespace-nowrap text-sm">Inclusivity</span> We strive to make our platform accessible and welcoming to people from all backgrounds.</li>
      <li class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4 shadow flex items-start gap-3"><span class="badge badge-accent badge-outline mt-1 whitespace-nowrap text-sm">Community</span> We believe in the power of shared knowledge and experiences.</li>
      <li class="bg-base-200 rounded-xl p-4 shadow flex items-start gap-3"><span class="badge badge-accent badge-outline mt-1 whitespace-nowrap text-sm">Privacy</span> We respect user privacy and maintain confidentiality.</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="divider my-8 before:bg-accent/20 after:bg-accent/20">What We Offer</div>

    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-8">
      <li class="mb-2">A Q&amp;A platform where users can ask questions about gender and receive thoughtful, informed responses.</li>
      <li class="mb-2">A knowledge base with resources on gender-related topics, derived from previously answered questions.</li>
      <li class="mb-2">A comprehensive terminology guide for simple questions of language.</li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mb-8">We believe that understanding gender diversity is essential for creating a more inclusive and accepting society. By providing accurate information and fostering meaningful dialogue, we hope to make things better for everyone.</p>

    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center mt-10">
      <%= link_to raw('<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 inline-block" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>Meet Our Team'), home_team_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-lg shadow" %>
      <%= link_to raw('<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 mr-2 inline-block" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4" /></svg>Get Involved'), home_volunteer_path, class: "btn btn-outline btn-lg shadow" %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>